            {
                "id": 4,
                "name": "XL",
                "description": "Gaining a new level increases [energy limit](/configure/item/5) and sets [current energy](/play/item/5?owner_id=13) to full.\r\n\r\nOn reaching level 3, see [Upgrade Bonus](/play/event/23?subject_id=13).\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\nLevel  Total XP Required\r\n~~~~~  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n1      (0)\r\n2      5\r\n3      15\r\n4      30\r\n5      50\r\n6      80\r\n7      120\r\n8      180\r\n9      260\r\n10     370\r\n11     500\r\n12     660\r\n13     860\r\n14     1110\r\n15     1400\r\n16     1800\r\n17     2300\r\n18     2900\r\n19     3600\r\n20     4200\r\n</pre>",
                "abilities": [],
                "is_binary": false,
                "enum_list": []
            }
