            {
                "id": 28,
                "name": "ATK Fist Pummel (To-Hit)",
                "description": "Close grasping digits and swing robotic arm forward. Basic melee attack.\r\n\r\n- **Energy**: The robot must have at least 1 to start. After the attack, consume 1 [Energy](/play/item/5?owner_id=13).\r\n- **Difficulty:** If you're significantly outleveled, for example level 1 or 2 to the enemy's 5, then set difficulty to *Hard*. If you significantly outlevel the opponent, then set difficulty to *Easy*.\r\n- **Damage:** If the attack hits then [Roll for Damage](/play/event/38?subject_id=13).\r\n- **Major Success:** (Nat 20) Roll two damage rolls instead of one.\r\n- **Major Failure:** Consume 2 Energy instead of 1.\r\n\r\nAfter the swing, the enemy gets to [take an action](/play/event/41) if they're still alive.",
